    "description": "A race against time, solve puzzles the fastest and make it to the end of the Musa Inc. Testing Facility and gain your freedom... from being a pineapple.<br><br>In <i>Radioactive Pineapple</i>, players have been “invited” to become a test subject of Musa Incorporated, a revolutionary company that wants humanity to evolve to a <i>peak potassium</i> state. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/97c2c1e2c0255df7645cf8fe4c870437.poster.avif?t=1721780212\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/97c2c1e2c0255df7645cf8fe4c870437.webm?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/97c2c1e2c0255df7645cf8fe4c870437.mp4?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Compete against the other pineapples in timed puzzles and challenges to gain access to the transformation potion first and return to your human form.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/db9df7ae53d9d7cd6d89a3222cf4d5d1.poster.avif?t=1721780212\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/db9df7ae53d9d7cd6d89a3222cf4d5d1.webm?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/db9df7ae53d9d7cd6d89a3222cf4d5d1.mp4?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your analytical skills to decipher different levels and uncover the hidden secret behind the test and attempt to beat your best time before you meet your juicy fate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/c6cfa3a360afef442db76023236b135c.poster.avif?t=1721780212\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/c6cfa3a360afef442db76023236b135c.webm?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/c6cfa3a360afef442db76023236b135c.mp4?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Play for free today!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/03d6a5e182ef3ddfcf0970c40e91c9b5.poster.avif?t=1721780212\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/03d6a5e182ef3ddfcf0970c40e91c9b5.webm?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058210/extras/03d6a5e182ef3ddfcf0970c40e91c9b5.mp4?t=1721780212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
